frames.caption: A cheerful astronaut sits in a futuristic vehicle on a rocky extraterrestrial landscape, holding a tablet. A rover is parked nearby under a clear blue sky with a distant planet visible.

The rover's design is sleek and advanced, suggesting exploration on an alien terrain.
